{"id":565473,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/08/【图说天朝】不同种族明码标价-欧洲白人价格/","date":"2017-08-03T02:13:29Z","modified":"2017-08-03T02:13:29Z","title":"【图说天朝】不同种族明码标价 “欧洲白人”价格最高","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>某家经营“外国人举牌”服务的网店，将不同种族的举牌者分级标价。其中“欧洲白人”价格最高，为30元，“亚洲华人”、“非洲黑人”、“印欧混血人”均报价20元。这也从侧面反映出中国民众对不同种族的普遍的态度。</p>\n<p>所谓的“外国人举牌／制作祝福视频”的服务似乎在中国越来越受欢迎，类似<a href=\"https://weibo.com/2243807243/Ff3Hgur4P\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">链接中这样</a>的“祝福视频”今后可能会越来越多。</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1639264641/FfhXpjquL\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@realEnjolras</a>：华夏儿女还是比较种族歧视 ​​​​</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smf4gihj20ku1124qp.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-565475\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smf4gihj20ku1124qp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smf4gihj20ku1124qp.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smf4gihj20ku1124qp-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smf4gihj20ku1124qp-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smeany4j20ku112n0e.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-565474\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smeany4j20ku112n0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smeany4j20ku112n0e.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smeany4j20ku112n0e-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/61b53181ly1fi5smeany4j20ku112n0e-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/67d17